{"tid":1270911,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"To所有想幫手但淆底既人","createTime":"2019-07-01T03:47:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T04:56:32.000Z","uid":42734,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ef605330a03f0657ffa7c18e64b94ffae9b68210","tid":1270911,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T03:47:41.000Z","msg":"唔好覺得自己無野做到，每個人都可以發揮自己既影響力，哪怕只係好微弱，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">星星之火，可以燎原！</span><br />\n<br />\n[勇士]For勇武的人：你地可以在前線直接與暴政抗衡<br />\n[示威者]For主張和平的人：你地可以幫手送物資、買物資<br />\n[鍵盤]For唔敢／唔比出街的人：你地可以幫手影響身邊朋友／家人、fb／ig 瘋狂share相關新聞，務求影響最多的人（唔洗怕自己會煩親人，如果有人因為呢d野覺得你煩，咁呢d朋友我覺得你可以盡早delete）<br />\n[美術]For略懂美術的人：你地可以幫手做文宣整單張之類宣傳下我地既訴求<br />\n[平民]For唔知自己可以做咩的人：幫手睇下有無義士失蹤，如果係附近最好真人去睇睇幫唔幫到手！有機會就用telegram之類聯絡下、安慰下各位同路人！順手留意下身邊人有無因為事件產生異樣！一個都不能少！！"},{"pid":"2f2a5c6045815349b3f80125fefdf23e3c9b62c5","tid":1270911,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T03:48:03.000Z","msg":"褲妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f9bb53a7e1f51b5a8f602c9f833943a70ce38cf","tid":1270911,"uid":42734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2f2a5c6045815349b3f80125fefdf23e3c9b62c5","tid":1270911,"uid":78683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T03:48:03.000Z","msg":"褲妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T03:49:02.000Z","msg":"肩！要平安"},{"pid":"cdf2d06e1c0f1f4041e7e4514a62f3da821dbdde","tid":1270911,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T03:50:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c391aae8eac22e4329e2084c2293a8e59cc9a253","tid":1270911,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdf2d06e1c0f1f4041e7e4514a62f3da821dbdde","tid":1270911,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T03:50:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T03:52:57.000Z","msg":"？？"},{"pid":"049e4a6ee9076fa25581